name: Chocolate Frosting Cupcake Jumping Blast Quest Pro
name_original: Chocolate Frosting Cupcake Jumping Blast Quest Pro
description:
Chocolate Frosting Cupcake Jumping Blast Quest Pro is an arcade game developed by Kristy Ashworth. It came out on 24-03-2014. It was published by Kristy Ashworth.
You can play Chocolate Frosting Cupcake Jumping Blast Quest Pro on iOS.
